held at 20:00 UTC in #spi on irc.spi-inc.org.
[LOG](../../../logs/2026/2026-03-09.txt).

## Treasurer's report

<pre>
Treasurer report. Processed payment queue at end of February. Missing
reimbursements are pending review.

If you have any urgency, please reach out.

Thanks very much for the continuous work of the treasurer team, including
president, vice-president and contractors.
</pre>

## Secretary's report

<pre>
So far, I have recorded 2026 Conflict of Interest forms from all but one
director, I'll reach out to the last one privately with a reminder.
</pre>

