## Items up for discussion

## Other business

* The board briefly touched upon ongoing discussions within multiple associated project communities about recent age verification laws in various jurisdictions. Kassia is engaging our legal counsel to start the process of getting recommendations.
* It was suggested, in order to maintain a timely workflow with regard to the steady stream of associated project applications, that: the number of outstanding applications be mentioned during the board meeting, and if no sponsor volunteers before the following meeting, then those applications will be politely declined.

## Adjournment

The meeting was adjourned until Monday April 13th, 2026 at 20:00 UTC
in #spi on irc.spi-inc.org.

